Notes: UW-L Holiday Inn Express Tip-Off Classic...Season-opener for both teams...
UW-L scores first nine points of game, leads by as many as 20 in 1st half...
Thirteen of 14 players score for UW-L, three in double figures...UW-L
outscores Alverno, 38-10, in paint...UW-L scores 36 points off turnovers.
